tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE workout_sessions (
  session_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  exercise_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  sets INT NOT NULL,
  reps INT NOT NULL,
  weights_used DECIMAL NOT NULL,
  duration_min INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE workout_sessions (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  exercise_type VARCHAR(50),
  sets INT,
  reps INT,
  weights_used FLOAT,
  duration_minutes INT
);

CREATE TABLE workout_logs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  weight_lifted FLOAT,
  duration_minutes INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES workout_sessions(session_id)
);

CREATE TABLE workout_sessions (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  exercise_type VARCHAR(255),
  sets INT,
  reps INT,
  weight_used DECIMAL,
  duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE workout_logs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID,
  user_id UUID,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES workout_sessions(session_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE WorkoutSessions (
    session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    exercise_type TEXT,
    sets INT,
    reps INT,
    weight_used DECIMAL,
    duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE Workouts (
    workout_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    session_id UUID,
    exercise_id UUID,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES Users(user_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES WorkoutSessions(session_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (exercise_id) REFERENCES Exercises(exercise_id)
);
CREATE TABLE exercises (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, exercise_name VARCHAR(100), sets INTEGER, reps INTEGER, weight FLOAT, duration INTERVAL);
CREATE TABLE workout_sessions (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, date TIMESTAMP, notes TEXT);
CREATE TABLE user_profiles (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(100), age INTEGER, height FLOAT, weight FLOAT);
CREATE TABLE user_workouts (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, user_id INTEGER, workout_id INTEGER, exercise_id INTEGER, sets INTEGER, reps INTEGER, weight FLOAT, duration INTERVAL);
CREATE TABLE workouts (id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY, workout_name VARCHAR(100));
